# ── Google Gemini (free tier) ───────────────────────────────────────
# Powers the AI product-description writer (Somali) and the public help
# assistant. Get a FREE API key at https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
# and paste it into .env.local. Without it, both features degrade gracefully
# (the describe button + assistant show a "not configured" message).

GEMINI_API_KEY=

# Optional — defaults to a free, fast multimodal model:
# GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.0-flash
